**Belongs / does not belong / editing discipline:** **core-po-product-docs** `SKILL.md` § **Normative**. **RouteName-first**; **no** Markdown links from **`app/**`** PO into **`servers/*`** / **`clients/*`** trees; run **`php .cursor/skills/core-docs-reader/check-doc-links.php app`** after PO edits.

**Shippable Laravel FeatureRoute surfaces:** PO + tests + **`RouteName::KNOWN_STATE`** lifecycle bar — **core-known-states** **`SKILL.md`** §6 (co-located triple, Pest/Playwright expectations, optional **`inventory-po-capsule-gaps.php`**). **Artisan-only** `extends Command` trees are out of scope for Inertia pairing.

