## Defaults (normative)

Doc placement, concern matrix, hub vs beside-the-code, **⬜/✅/❌** legend: **core-structure-and-naming** `structure.md` (**§ Product shape at a glance**, **§ Normative rules**). Reviewer taste: **core-comments**. **Normative first** → cited stems + portable batch; **contracts first** → portable law before wide product edits.

