## Verify and merge requests

**PR body commands, green batch vs rows, operator-facing Laravel UI bar:** **core-review-pr** `SKILL.md` (**§ PR evidence**, **§ Operator-facing Laravel UI closure**). Layer **V1–V5**: **core-verify-pr** + **core-tpm-delegate**.

## Read order (implementers) — pointer

No PO anchor → stop. Then: linked **PO** → **IDENTITY** / product-shape when naming matters → **cited stem prose** (not green alone) → **stack verify** + ops runbook for **your** stack → prove via **contract** / **structure** / portable batch / stack verify / **`./mono check`** as scope dictates. **Detail:** **core-implement-slice** `SKILL.md`.

